CREATE PROCEDURE dbo.testscoring1030
AS
BEGIN

SELECT
    CAST([productCode] AS [float]) AS [productCode],
    CAST([price] AS [float]) AS [price],
    CAST([advertising] AS [float]) AS [advertising],
    CAST([storeId] AS [float]) AS [storeId],
    CAST([weekStarting] AS [float]) AS [weekStarting],
    CAST([wholeSaleCost] AS [float]) AS [wholeSaleCost],
    CAST([basePrice] AS [float]) AS [basePrice],
    CAST([income] AS [float]) AS [income],
    CAST([minoritiesRatio] AS [float]) AS [minoritiesRatio],
    CAST([largeHH] AS [float]) AS [largeHH],
    CAST([highIncome150Ratio] AS [float]) AS [highIncome150Ratio],
    CAST([more1FullTimeEmployeeRatio] AS [float]) AS [more1FullTimeEmployeeRatio],
    CAST([ratioAge60] AS [float]) AS [ratioAge60],
    CAST([salesNearestWarehousesRatio] AS [float]) AS [salesNearestWarehousesRatio],
    CAST([salesNearest5StoresRatio] AS [float]) AS [salesNearest5StoresRatio],
    CAST([collegeRatio] AS [float]) AS [collegeRatio],
    CAST([avgDistanceNearest5Supermarkets] AS [float]) AS [avgDistanceNearest5Supermarkets],
    CAST([distanceNearestWarehouse] AS [float]) AS [distanceNearestWarehouse]
INTO [dbo].[#retail_scoring_data]
FROM [dbo].[retail_scoring_data];

SELECT *
FROM PREDICT (MODEL = (SELECT [model] FROM dbo.AMLModels WHERE [ID] = 'synapse_retail_model_hb:4'),
              DATA = [dbo].[retail_scoring_data_1101]) WITH ([quantity] [float])

END
GO

EXEC dbo.testscoring1030
